#

Ultimate Beef Burger Feast

$25
800 kcal

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinComfort Food

Tags:

BeefBurgersAmerican Cuisine

Description

Juicy, flavorful burgers made from fresh ground beef, served with crispy fries and a side of creamy coleslaw.

Ingredients

  • Ground Beef: 6 lb
  • Burger Buns: 12
  • Cheddar Cheese: 12 slices
  • Lettuce: 1 head
  • Tomato: 3 large
  • Onion: 2 medium
  • Pickles: 1 jar
  • Ketchup: 1 cup
  • Mustard: 1/2 cup
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Potatoes: 4 large
  • Olive Oil: 1/4 cup
  • Coleslaw Mix: 1 bag
  • Coleslaw Dressing: 1 cup
